      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This used car is in poor condition and needs significant attention. The exterior has noticeable dents, scratches, and rust in multiple areas. The interior shows heavy wear including torn upholstery and damaged trim. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require repair before reliable daily use \u2014 sold as-is.",
